## ğŸ§© **5. The Operating System (OS)**

The OS is the **bridge between hardware & applications**.

### ğŸ”§ **5.1 Responsibilities of the OS**

* Process scheduling
* Memory allocation
* File system management
* Hardware communication
* Security & user permissions
* Networking

